fix: address 21 PR review comments + 3 critical gameplay bugs

Issues fixed:
1. 60s countdown persists across app restarts (server-side timer)
2. All-bots games auto-delete when timer expires (banner resets)
3. Replacement bots now play correctly (room_players.id lookup)

PR review comments addressed:
- Security: REVOKE from PUBLIC/anon on all SECURITY DEFINER RPCs
- update-heartbeat: ownership check, update count, heartbeat_count default
- useConnectionManager: single-condition Realtime filter
- RejoinModal: onRequestClose for Android back button
- Migration: remove unused variables
- play-cards/player-pass: service-role lookup by room_players.id
